tadata":{"preview":"# AR-043 — 架构设计文档与 API 文档 Design\n\n## Overview\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-043 — 架构设计文档与 API 文档 |\n| Module | docs |\n| Language | Markdown |\n| Size | M |\n| Stage | ST-1 |\n\n---\n\n## Architecture\n\n[TO BE FILLED: Add architecture overview]\n\n---\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-043/design.md","time":{"start":1775906232878,"end":1775906232888}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775906232892,"sessionID":"ses_283be1a44ffeIL7jHPe1xT3iWR","part":{"id":"prt_d7c429a1a001rpdtVSET7YzyZ6","messageID":"msg_d7c42863b001OEfYG0UcUayqQY","sessionID":"ses_283be1a44ffeIL7jHPe1xT3iWR","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-cc6bcb64082a4cb39cb88c9a88aaaff4","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-043/proposal.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-043/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-043 — 架构设计文档与 API 文档\n2: \n3: ## 概述\n4: \n5: | 属性 | 值 |\n6: |------|-----|\n7: | AR | AR-043 |\n8: | Module | docs |\n9: | Language | Markdown |\n10: | Size | M |\n11: \n12: ---\n13: \n14: ## 1. Purpose (目的)\n15: \n16: 为 AgentCube 系统建立完整的架构设计文档和 API 文档体系，确保：\n17: \n18: - **架构透明性**：提供清晰的系统架构视图，帮助开发者快速理解 AgentCube 的设计理念和组件交互\n19: - **API 可发现性**：为所有公开 API（Router、WorkloadManager、PicoD）提供标准化 OpenAPI 规范，支持 API 探索和客户端集成\n20: - **CRD 文档化**：为 `AgentRuntime` 和 `CodeInterpreter` CRD 提供详细字段说明和使用示例\n21: - **SDK API 参考**：为 Python SDK 和 client-go 提供完整的 API 参考文档\n22: - **开发者体验**：降低新开发者上手门槛，减少因文档缺失导致的集成问题\n23: \n24: ---\n25: \n26: ## 2. Scope (范围)\n27: \n28: ### 2.1 In Scope\n29: \n30: | Deliverable | Description |\n31: |-------------|-------------|\n32: | `docs/docs/architecture/overview.md` | AgentCube 系统整体架构概览，包含四层架构图、组件职责、交互流程 |\n33: | `docs/docs/architecture/components.md` | 四大核心组件详细设计：Router、WorkloadManager、PicoD、Agentd |\n34: | `docs/docs/architecture/crds.md` | AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter CRD 设计文档，包含字段定义、状态机、生命周期图 |\n35: | `docs/docs/architecture/session-flow.md` | Session 创建、路由、销毁完整流程图和时序说明 |\n36: | `docs/docs/architecture/data-flow.md` | 数据流向图：请求→Router→Sandbox→响应的完整数据路径 |\n37: | `docs/docs/api/router/openapi.yaml` | Router HTTP API OpenAPI 3.0 规范（Health、Invocation Proxy、Session 端点） |\n38: | `docs/docs/api/workloadmanager/openapi.yaml` | WorkloadManager HTTP API OpenAPI 3.0 规范（Health、Sandbox CRUD 端点） |\n39: | `docs/docs/api/picod/openapi.yaml` | PicoD HTTP API OpenAPI 3.0 规范（Execute、Files、Health 端点） |\n40: | `docs/docs/api/sdk-python/sdk-python-api.md` | Python SDK API 参考文档（CodeInterpreterClient、AgentRuntimeClient） |\n41: | `docs/docs/api/client-go/client-go-api.md` | client-go API 参考文档（typed client、informer、lister） |\n42: | `docs/docs/api/crds/agent-runtime.md` | AgentRuntime CRD API 参考文档 |\n43: | `docs/docs/api/crds/code-interpreter.md` | CodeInterpreter CRD API 参考文档 |\n44: | `docs/docusaurus.config.js` 更新 | 配置侧边栏导航，整合架构和 API 文档分类 |\n45: \n46: ### 2.2 Out of Scope\n47: \n48: | Item | Reason |\n49: |------|--------|\n50: | 性能基准文档 | 性能测试数据属于专项 AR，待测试完成后补充 |\n51: | 安全最佳实践文档 | 安全文档属于独立模块，后续专项处理 |\n52: | 运维手册 | 运维操作手册（故障排查、升级流程）属于独立 AR |\n53: | 多语言文档翻译 | 初始版本仅提供英文文档，翻译作为后续迭代 |\n54: | API 自动生成工具集成 | OpenAPI 规范手工编写，自动生成工具集成作为后续优化 |\n55: | Interactive API Explorer | Swagger UI 集成作为后续增强 |\n56: \n57: ---\n58: \n59: ## 3. Impact Analysis (影响分析)\n60: \n61: ### 3.1 新增文件\n62: \n63: | File | Description |\n64: |------|-------------|\n65: | `docs/docs/architecture/overview.md` | 系统架构总览，包含四层架构图、部署拓扑、组件职责矩阵 |\n66: | `docs/docs/architecture/components.md` | Router、WorkloadManager、PicoD、Agentd 组件详细设计文档 |\n67: | `docs/docs/architecture/crds.md` | AgentRuntime、CodeInterpreter CRD 设计文档 |\n68: | `docs/docs/architecture/session-flow.md` | Session 生命周期流程图和时序说明 |\n69: | `docs/docs/architecture/data-flow.md` | 数据流向图和请求处理流程 |\n70: | `docs/docs/api/router/openapi.yaml` | Router OpenAPI 3.0 规范文件 |\n71: | `docs/docs/api/workloadmanager/openapi.yaml` | WorkloadManager OpenAPI 3.0 规范文件 |\n72: | `docs/docs/api/picod/openapi.yaml` | PicoD OpenAPI 3.0 规范文件 |\n73: | `docs/docs/api/sdk-python/sdk-python-api.md` | Python SDK API 参考文档 |\n74: | `docs/docs/api/client-go/client-go-api.md` | client-go API 参考文档 |\n75: | `docs/docs/api/crds/agent-runtime.md` | AgentRuntime CRD API 文档 |\n76: | `docs/docs/api/crds/code-interpreter.md` | CodeInterpreter CRD API 文档 |\n77: | `docs/docs/api/_category_.json` | API 文档分类配置 |\n78: | `docs/docs/architecture/_category_.json` | 架构文档分类配置 |\n79: | `docs/docs/api/crds/_category_.json` | CRD API 分类配置 |\n80: \n81: ### 3.2 修改文件\n82: \n83: | File | Change |\n84: |------|--------|\n85: | `docs/docusaurus.config.js` | 新增架构和 API 侧边栏导航配置 |\n86: | `docs/sidebars.js` | 新增架构和 API 文档侧边栏结构 |\n87: | `docs/docs/getting-started/next-steps.md` | 更新\"下一步\"链接指向架构和 API 文档 |\n88: \n89: ### 3.3 Upstream Dependencies\n90: \n91: | Dependency | Purpose |\n92: |------------|---------|\n93: | Docusaurus 3.x | 文档站点框架（已有） |\n94: | OpenAPI 3.0 Spec | API 规范格式标准 |\n95: | Mermaid JS | 架构图和流程图渲染（Docusaurus 插件） |\n96: | design.md (根目录) | 系统设计文档（架构文档输入源） |\n97: | pkg/router | Router API 实现代码（API 文档输入源） |\n98: | pkg/workloadmanager | WorkloadManager API 实现代码 |\n99: | pkg/picod | PicoD API 实现代码 |\n100: | sdk-python | Python SDK 源代码（SDK API 文档输入源） |\n101: | client-go | Go client 源代码（client-go API 文档输入源） |\n102: \n103: ### 3.4 Downstream Consumers\n104: \n105: | Consumer | Usage |\n106: |----------|-------|\n107: | 开发者 | 通过架构文档理解系统设计，通过 API 文档集成系统 |\n108: | SDK 用户 | 参考 SDK API 文档进行客户端开发 |\n109: | 平台运维 | 通过架构文档理解组件交互和故障定位 |\n110: | CI/CD Pipeline | 验证 OpenAPI 规范与实现一致性 |\n111: | 外部集成方 | 通过 OpenAPI 规范进行第三方集成 |\n112: \n113: ---\n114: \n115: ## 4. Alternatives Considered (备选方案)\n116: \n117: ### 4.1 手工编写 OpenAPI vs 自动生成\n118: \n119: **手工编写**：\n120: | Aspect | Evaluation |\n121: |--------|------------|\n122: | 优点 | 完全控制文档内容，可添加详细示例、说明；无代码生成依赖 |\n123: | 缺点 | 需手动维护与代码同步；可能出现文档与实现不一致 |\n124: | 适用场景 | MVP 阶段、文档优先级高于代码约束 |\n125: \n126: **自动生成（swaggo/swag, go-swagger）**：\n127: | Aspect | Evaluation |\n128: |--------|------------|\n129: | 优点 | 文档与代码自动同步；减少手动维护成本 |\n130: | 缺点 | 需要在代码中添加 annotation；生成的文档可能不够详细；需要额外工具链 |\n131: | 适用场景 | 大规模项目、频繁 API 变更 |\n132: \n133: **决策**：采用手工编写 OpenAPI 规范，原因：\n134: 1. AgentCube API 相对稳定，变更频率可控\n135: 2. MVP 阶段优先保证文档质量和可读性\n136: 3. 可添加丰富的示例和说明，提升开发者体验\n137: 4. 后续迭代可考虑自动生成工具集成\n138: \n139: ### 4.2 独立 API 文档站点 vs 集成到主文档站点\n140: \n141: **独立站点（Swagger UI / Redoc）**：\n142: | Aspect | Evaluation |\n143: |--------|------------|\n144: | 优点 | 专业 API Explorer 界面；支持 Try It Out；独立部署 |\n145: | 缺点 | 文档分散；用户需访问多个站点；维护成本增加 |\n146: | 适用场景 | 纯 API 产品、大量公开 API |\n147: \n148: **集成到主站点（Docusaurus）**：\n149: | Aspect | Evaluation |\n150: |--------|------------|\n151: | 优点 | 文档集中统一；一致的导航体验；单一部署单元 |\n152: | 缺点 | Try It Out 功能较弱；需要额外配置 |\n153: | 适用场景 | 综合文档站点、产品文档与 API 文档并存 |\n154: \n155: **决策**：集成到 Docusaurus 主文档站点，原因：\n156: 1. AgentCube 是综合系统，架构文档与 API 文档需要并存\n157: 2. 统一的导航体验降低用户认知成本\n158: 3. 后续可通过插件支持 Swagger UI 嵌入\n159: \n160: ### 4.3 Mermaid vs PlantUML vs ASCII Art\n161: \n162: **Mermaid**：\n163: | Aspect | Evaluation |\n164: |--------|------------|\n165: | 优点 | Markdown 内嵌；Docusaurus 原生支持；渲染效果好；易于维护 |\n166: | 缺点 | 复杂图形支持有限；需要特定语法 |\n167: | 适用场景 | 流程图、时序图、架构图 |\n168: \n169: **PlantUML**：\n170: | Aspect | Evaluation |\n171: |--------|------------|\n172: | 优点 | 功能强大；支持复杂图形；丰富图表类型 |\n173: | 缺点 | 需要外部渲染；Docusaurus 集成复杂；维护成本高 |\n174: | 适用场景 | UML 类图、复杂架构图 |\n175: \n176: **ASCII Art**：\n177: | Aspect | Evaluation |\n178: |--------|------------|\n179: | 优点 | 无渲染依赖；任何环境可读 |\n180: | 缺点 | 美观度差；编辑困难；复杂图形难以表达 |\n181: | 适用场景 | 简单示意图、README 文档 |\n182: \n183: **决策**：采用 Mermaid，原因：\n184: 1. Docusaurus 原生支持 Mermaid 插件\n185: 2. 架构图、流程图、时序图均可表达\n186: 3. Markdown 内嵌，易于版本控制和协作编辑\n187: \n188: ### 4.4 单一架构文档 vs 多模块架构文档\n189: \n190: **单一文档（architecture.md）**：\n191: | Aspect | Evaluation |\n192: |--------|------------|\n193: | 优点 | 简单结构；单一导航入口 |\n194: | 缺点 | 文档过长；难以维护；搜索困难 |\n195: | 适用场景 | 小型系统、简单架构 |\n196: \n197: **多模块文档（overview, components, crds, flows）**：\n198: | Aspect | Evaluation |\n199: |--------|------------|\n200: | 优点 | 模块化结构；易于维护；细粒度导航；独立更新 |\n201: | 缺点 | 文档分散；需要侧边栏配置 |\n202: | 适用场景 | 中大型系统、复杂架构 |\n203: \n204: **决策**：采用多模块架构文档，原因：\n205: 1. AgentCube 有四大核心组件，每个组件需要详细说明\n206: 2. CRD、Session Flow、Data Flow 属于独立主题\n207: 3. 模块化文档便于后续扩展和维护\n208: \n209: ---\n210: \n211: ## 5. Risks\n212: \n213: | Risk | Mitigation |\n214: |------|------------|\n215: | OpenAPI 规范与实现不一致 | 定期手动审查 API 实现与文档一致性；CI 增加 API spec 校验步骤 |\n216: | 架构图与实际部署拓扑不符 | 架构图基于 design.md 源文件，随设计文档同步更新 |\n217: | 文档过时影响开发者体验 | 建立\"文档更新检查\"流程，每次 API 变更触发文档 review |\n218: | Mermaid 渲染失败 | 确保所有 Mermaid 语法正确；提供纯文本 fallback |\n219: | SDK API 文档缺失关键方法 | 参考 SDK 源代码完整枚举所有公开方法 |\n220: \n221: ---\n222: \n223: ## 6. Implementation Checklist\n224: \n225: - [ ] 创建 `docs/docs/architecture/` 目录结构\n226: - [ ] 编写 `architecture/overview.md` — 系统架构总览\n227: - [ ] 编写 `architecture/components.md` — 四大组件详细设计\n228: - [ ] 编写 `architecture/crds.md` — CRD 设计文档\n229: - [ ] 编写 `architecture/session-flow.md` — Session 流程图\n230: - [ ] 编写 `architecture/data-flow.md` — 数据流向图\n231: - [ ] 创建 `docs/docs/api/router/` 目录\n232: - [ ] 编写 `api/router/openapi.yaml` — Router API 规范\n233: - [ ] 创建 `docs/docs/api/workloadmanager/` 目录\n234: - [ ] 编写 `api/workloadmanager/openapi.yaml` — WorkloadManager API 规范\n235: - [ ] 创建 `docs/docs/api/picod/` 目录\n236: - [ ] 编写 `api/picod/openapi.yaml` — PicoD API 规范\n237: - [ ] 编写 `api/sdk-python/sdk-python-api.md` — Python SDK API 参考\n238: - [ ] 编写 `api/client-go/client-go-api.md` — client-go API 参考\n239: - [ ] 创建 `docs/docs/api/crds/` 目录\n240: - [ ] 编写 `api/crds/agent-runtime.md` — AgentRuntime CRD 文档\n241: - [ ] 编写 `api/crds/code-interpreter.md` — CodeInterpreter CRD 文档\n242: - [ ] 创建各目录 `_category_.json` 分类配置\n243: - [ ] 更新 `docusaurus.config.js` 侧边栏配置\n244: - [ ] 更新 `sidebars.js` 导航结构\n245: - [ ] 更新 `getting-started/next-steps.md` 链接\n246: - [ ] 本地预览验证文档渲染正确\n247: - [ ] 验证 Mermaid 图表渲染\n248: \n249: ---\n250: \n251: ## 7. References\n252: \n253: - [Design Document](../../design.md)\n254: - [Project Context](../../project.md)\n255: - [Router Package](../../pkg/router/)\n256: - [WorkloadManager Package](../../pkg/workloadmanager/)\n257: - [PicoD Package](../../pkg/picod/)\n258: - [Python SDK](../../sdk-python/)\n259: - [client-go](../../client-go/)\n260: - [Docusaurus Documentation](https://docusaurus.io/docs)\n261: - [OpenAPI Specification 3.0](https://spec.openapis.org/oas/v3.0.0)\n262: - [Mermaid Documentation](https://mermaid.js.org/)\n\n(End of file - total 262 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-043 — 架构设计文档与 API 文档\n\n## 概述\n\n| 属性 | 值 |\n|------|-----|\n| AR | AR-043 |\n| Module | docs |\n| Language | Markdown |\n| Size | M |\n\n---\n\n## 1. Purpose (目的)\n\n为 AgentCube 系统建立完整的架构设计文档和 API 文档体系，确保：\n\n- **架构透明性**：提供清晰的系统架构视图，帮助开发者快速理解 AgentCube 的设计理念和组件交互\n- **API 可发现性**：为所有公开 API（Router、WorkloadManager、PicoD）提供标准化 OpenAPI 规范，支持 API 探索和客户端集成\n- **CRD 文档化**：为 `AgentRuntime` 和 `CodeInterpreter` CRD 提供详细字段说明和使用示例","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-043/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775906232880,"end":1775906232890}}}}
{"type":"step_finish","timestamp":1775906232920,"sessionID":"ses_283be1a44ffeIL7jHPe1xT3iWR","part":{"id":"prt_d7c429a3c001gv0xCr0kBWvIQl","reason":"tool-calls","snapshot":"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114","messageID":"msg_d7c42863b001OEfYG0UcUayqQY","sessionID":"ses_283be1a44ffeIL7jHPe1xT3iWR","type":"step-finish","tokens":{"total":52662,"input":1585,"output":134,"reasoning":0,"cache":{"write":0,"read":50943}},"cost":0}}
{"type":"step_start","timestamp":1775906236196,"sessionID":"ses_283be1a44ffeIL7jHPe1xT3iWR","part":{"id":"prt_d7c42a723001dnJjXxG3zAJiHo","messageID":"msg_d7c429a74001p1vX3gn1PFRLia","sessionID":"ses_283be1a44ffeIL7jHPe1xT3iWR","snapshot":"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114","type":"step-start"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775906441801,"sessionID":"ses_283be1a44ffeIL7jHPe1xT3iWR","part":{"id":"prt_d7c45c9b50012aBxGGUJHJ4YKn","messageID":"msg_d7c429a74001p1vX3gn1PFRLia","sessionID":"ses_283be1a44ffeIL7jHPe1xT3iWR","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-8097420efd1a4d9babc2ebd67016b476","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-043/design.md","content":"# AR-043 — 架构设计文档与 API 文档 Design\n\n## Overview\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-043 — 架构设计文档与 API 文档 |\n| Module | docs |\n| Language | Markdown |\n| Size | M |\n| Stage | ST-1 (Completed) |\n\n---\n\n## Architecture\n\n### System Overview\n\nAgentCube is a Kubernetes-native sandbox orchestration platform for AI agents. It provides on-demand provisioning of isolated sandbox pods, session-aware HTTP routing, and lifecycle management (creation, expiry, idle cleanup).\n\n### Four-Layer Architecture\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                          Layer 1: Client Interface                               │\n├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n│  ┌─────────────┐    ┌─────────────┐    ┌─────────────┐                         │\n│  │ Python SDK  │    │ client-go   │    │   CLI Tool  │                         │\n│  │ (FastAPI)   │    │ (typed)     │    │  (Typer)    │                         │\n│  └─────────────┘    └─────────────┘    └─────────────┘                         │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n                                      │\n                                      ▼\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                          Layer 2: Gateway Layer                                  │\n├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n│  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐   │\n│  │                           Router (Deployment)                             │   │\n│  │  - Session routing and reverse proxy                                      │   │\n│  │  - JWT RS256 authentication                                                │   │\n│  │  - Concurrency limiting middleware                                         │   │\n│  │  - Health endpoints: /health/live, /health/ready                          │   │\n│  │  Port: :8080 (Gin framework)                                              │   │\n│  └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘   │\n│                                      │                                          │\n│                                      ▼                                          │\n│  ┌─────────────────┐                                                       │   │\n│  │ Redis/Valkey    │  Session Store (session-id → sandbox mapping)        │   │\n│  │ (Port 6379)     │  TTL-based expiry, last activity tracking            │   │\n│  └─────────────────┘                                                       │   │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n                                      │\n                                      ▼\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                          Layer 3: Management Layer                               │\n├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n│  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐   │\n│  │                     WorkloadManager (Deployment)                          │   │\n│  │  - Sandbox lifecycle management (Create/Get/Delete)                       │   │\n│  │  - Kubernetes CRD informers (AgentRuntime, CodeInterpreter)               │   │\n│  │  - Garbage collector for expired/idle sandboxes                           │   │\n│  │  Port: :8080 (Chi framework)                                              │   │\n│  └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘   │\n│                                      │                                          │\n│                                      ▼                                          │\n│  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐   │\n│  │                           Agentd (Deployment)                              │   │\n│  │  - Idle cleanup controller (controller-runtime)                           │   │\n│  │  - Leader election enabled                                                │   │\n│  │  - Watches AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter resources                    │   │\n│  └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘   │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n                                      │\n                                      ▼\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                          Layer 4: Sandbox Layer                                  │\n├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n│  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐   │\n│  │                        Sandbox Pod (per session)                          │   │\n│  │  ┌─────────────────┐    ┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐      │   │\n│  │  │ PicoD (Sidecar) │    │  Main Container (Agent/Application)    │      │   │\n│  │  │ Port: 8080      │    │  - User-defined workload               │      │   │\n│  │  │ - Execute code  │    │  - HTTP/HTTPS endpoints                │      │   │\n│  │  │ - File I/O      │    │                                        │      │   │\n│  │  │ - Auth middleware│    │                                        │      │   │\n│  │  └─────────────────┘    └─────────────────────────────────────────┘      │   │\n│  └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘   │\n│                                                                                 │\n│  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐   │\n│  │                     Warm Pool Pods (CodeInterpreter)                      │   │\n│  │  - Pre-warmed sandbox instances ready for immediate allocation            │   │\n│  │  - Configurable warm pool size per CodeInterpreter                        │   │\n│  └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘   │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n### Component Responsibilities\n\n| Component | Package | HTTP Framework | Primary Responsibility |\n|-----------|---------|----------------|------------------------|\n| Router | `pkg/router` | Gin | Session routing, reverse proxy, JWT auth |\n| WorkloadManager | `pkg/workloadmanager` | Chi | Sandbox CRUD, lifecycle management, GC |\n| PicoD | `pkg/picod` | Gin | Local code execution, file I/O in sandbox |\n| Agentd | `pkg/agentd` | controller-runtime | Idle cleanup controller with leader election |\n| Store | `pkg/store` | - | Redis/Valkey session storage abstraction |\n\n### Deployment Topology\n\n```\n┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                         Kubernetes Cluster                                         │\n├──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n│                                                                                   │\n│  Namespace: default (or user-defined)                                            │\n│                                                                                   │\n│  ┌─────────────────────────┐    ┌─────────────────────────┐                     │\n│  │ router Deployment       │    │ workloadmanager Deployment│                    │\n│  │ Replicas: 2+            │    │ Replicas: 1              │                     │\n│  │ Port: 8080              │    │ Port: 8080               │                     │\n│  │ Service: ClusterIP      │    │ Service: ClusterIP       │                     │\n│  └─────────────────────────┘    └─────────────────────────┘                     │\n│                                                                                   │\n│  ┌─────────────────────────┐    ┌─────────────────────────┐                     │\n│  │ agentd Deployment       │    │ Redis/Valkey StatefulSet│                     │\n│  │ Replicas: 1             │    │ Port: 6379              │                     │\n│  │ Leader Election: true   │    │ Persistence: enabled    │                     │\n│  └─────────────────────────┘    └─────────────────────────┘                     │\n│                                                                                   │\n│  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐     │\n│  │ Sandbox Pods (dynamic, per session)                                      │     │\n│  │ Labels:                                                                  │     │\n│  │   - runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/owner-runtime=<name>                   │     │\n│  │   - runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/owner-kind=<AgentRuntime/CodeInterpreter>│     │\n│  │   - runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/session-id=<session-id>                │     │\n│  │ Annotations:                                                              │     │\n│  │   - runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/auth-mode=<picod/none>                 │     │\n│  │   - runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/session-start=<timestamp>              │     │\n│  │   - runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/last-activity=<timestamp>              │     │\n│  └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘     │\n│                                                                                   │\n│  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐     │\n│  │ CRDs (runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1)                             │     │\n│  │   - AgentRuntime                                                         │     │\n│  │   - CodeInterpreter                                                      │     │\n│  └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘     │\n│                                                                                   │\n└──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n---\n\n## Data Structures\n\n### CRD Types\n\n#### AgentRuntime (pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime_types.go)\n\n```go\ntype AgentRuntime struct {\n    metav1.TypeMeta   `json:\",inline\"`\n    metav1.ObjectMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n    Spec   AgentRuntimeSpec   `json:\"spec\"`\n    Status AgentRuntimeStatus `json:\"status,omitempty\"`\n}\n\ntype AgentRuntimeSpec struct {\n    Ports              []TargetPort       `json:\"targetPort\"`       // Network ports to expose\n    Template           *SandboxTemplate   `json:\"podTemplate\"`      // Pod template for sandbox\n    SessionTimeout     *metav1.Duration   `json:\"sessionTimeout\"`   // Idle timeout (default: 15m)\n    MaxSessionDuration *metav1.Duration   `json:\"maxSessionDuration\"` // Max session life (default: 8h)\n}\n\ntype AgentRuntimeStatus struct {\n    Conditions []metav1.Condition `json:\"conditions,omitempty\"`\n}\n\ntype SandboxTemplate struct {\n    Labels      map[string]string `json:\"labels,omitempty\"`\n    Annotations map[string]string `json:\"annotations,omitempty\"`\n    Spec        corev1.PodSpec    `json:\"spec\"`\n}\n```\n\n#### CodeInterpreter (pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go)\n\n```go\ntype CodeInterpreter struct {\n    metav1.TypeMeta   `json:\",inline\"`\n    metav1.ObjectMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n    Spec   CodeInterpreterSpec   `json:\"spec\"`\n    Status CodeInterpreterStatus `json:\"status,omitempty\"`\n}\n\ntype CodeInterpreterSpec struct {\n    Ports              []TargetPort                    `json:\"ports,omitempty\"`\n    Template           *CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate `json:\"template\"`\n    SessionTimeout     *metav1.Duration                `json:\"sessionTimeout,omitempty\"`\n    MaxSessionDuration *metav1.Duration                `json:\"maxSessionDuration,omitempty\"`\n    WarmPoolSize       *int32                          `json:\"warmPoolSize,omitempty\"`\n    AuthMode           AuthModeType                    `json:\"authMode,omitempty\"` // picod | none\n}\n\ntype CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate struct {\n    Labels           map[string]string            `json:\"labels,omitempty\"`\n    Annotations      map[string]string            `json:\"annotations,omitempty\"`\n    RuntimeClassName *string                      `json:\"runtimeClassName,omitempty\"`\n    Image            string                       `json:\"image,omitempty\"`\n    ImagePullPolicy  corev1.PullPolicy            `json:\"imagePullPolicy,omitempty\"`\n    ImagePullSecrets []corev1.LocalObjectReference `json:\"imagePullSecrets,omitempty\"`\n    Environment      []corev1.EnvVar              `json:\"environment,omitempty\"`\n    Command          []string                     `json:\"command,omitempty\"`\n    Args             []string                     `json:\"args,omitempty\"`\n    Resources        corev1.ResourceRequirements  `json:\"resources,omitempty\"`\n}\n\ntype CodeInterpreterStatus struct {\n    Conditions []metav1.Condition `json:\"conditions,omitempty\"`\n    Ready      bool               `json:\"ready,omitempty\"`\n}\n```\n\n#### Shared Types (pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types.go)\n\n```go\ntype TargetPort struct {\n    PathPrefix string       `json:\"pathPrefix,omitempty\"` // URL path prefix for routing\n    Name       string       `json:\"name,omitempty\"`       // Human-readable port name\n    Port       uint32       `json:\"port\"`                 // Container port number\n    Protocol   ProtocolType `json:\"protocol\"`             // HTTP | HTTPS\n}\n\ntype ProtocolType string\nconst (\n    ProtocolTypeHTTP  ProtocolType = \"HTTP\"\n    ProtocolTypeHTTPS ProtocolType = \"HTTPS\"\n)\n\ntype AuthModeType string\nconst (\n    AuthModePicoD AuthModeType = \"picod\"\n    AuthModeNone AuthModeType = \"none\"\n)\n```\n\n#### Label/Annotation Constants\n\n```go\nconst (\n    LabelKeyOwnerRuntime    = \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/owner-runtime\"\n    LabelKeyOwnerKind       = \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/owner-kind\"\n    LabelKeySessionID       = \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/session-id\"\n    LabelKeySandboxType     = \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/sandbox-type\"\n    \n    AnnotationKeyAuthMode       = \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/auth-mode\"\n    AnnotationKeySessionStart   = \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/session-start\"\n    AnnotationKeySessionEnd     = \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/session-end\"\n    AnnotationKeyLastActivity   = \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/last-activity\"\n    AnnotationKeyWarmPoolMember = \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/warm-pool-member\"\n)\n```\n\n### Sandbox Info (pkg/common/types/sandbox.go)\n\n```go\ntype CreateSandboxRequest struct {\n    Kind      string `json:\"kind\"`      // AgentRuntime | CodeInterpreter\n    Name      string `json:\"name\"`      // CR name\n    Namespace string `json:\"namespace\"` // CR namespace\n}\n\ntype CreateSandboxResponse struct {\n    SessionID   string              `json:\"sessionId\"`\n    SandboxID   string              `json:\"sandboxId\"`\n    SandboxName string              `json:\"sandboxName\"`\n    EntryPoints []SandboxEntryPoint `json:\"entryPoints\"`\n}\n\ntype SandboxEntryPoint struct {\n    Path     string `json:\"path\"`     // URL path\n    Protocol string `json:\"protocol\"` // HTTP | HTTPS\n    Endpoint string `json:\"endpoint\"` // Target endpoint URL\n}\n\ntype SandboxInfo struct {\n    Kind               string              `json:\"kind\"`\n    SandboxID          string              `json:\"sandboxId\"`\n    SandboxNamespace   string              `json:\"sandboxNamespace\"`\n    SandboxName        string              `json:\"sandboxName\"`\n    Name               string              `json:\"name\"`            // CR name\n    SessionID          string              `json:\"sessionId\"`\n    CreatedAt          time.Time           `json:\"createdAt\"`\n    ExpiresAt          time.Time           `json:\"expiresAt\"`\n    Status             string              `json:\"status\"`\n    EntryPoints        []SandboxEntryPoint `json:\"entryPoints\"`\n    UserToken          string              `json:\"userToken,omitempty\"`\n    ServiceAccount     string              `json:\"serviceAccount,omitempty\"`\n    ServiceAccountName string              `json:\"serviceAccountName,omitempty\"`\n    LastActivity       time.Time           `json:\"lastActivity,omitempty\"`\n}\n```\n\n### Router Types (pkg/router)\n\n```go\ntype RouterClaims struct {\n    SessionID string `json:\"session_id\"`\n    SandboxID string `json:\"sandbox_id\"`\n    Namespace string `json:\"namespace\"`\n    Name      string `json:\"name\"`\n    jwt.RegisteredClaims\n}\n\ntype TokenPair struct {\n    AccessToken  string `json:\"access_token\"`\n    RefreshToken string `json:\"refresh_token\"`\n    ExpiresIn    int64  `json:\"expires_in\"`\n    TokenType    string `json:\"token_type\"`\n}\n```\n\n### WorkloadManager Types (pkg/workloadmanager/types.go)\n\n```go\ntype ErrorResponse struct {\n    Code    string `json:\"code\"`\n    Message string `json:\"message\"`\n    Details any    `json:\"details,omitempty\"`\n}\n\ntype SuccessResponse struct {\n    Data any `json:\"data\"`\n}\n\ntype ValidationError struct {\n    Field  string\n    Reason string\n}\n\ntype NotFoundError struct {\n    Resource string\n    Name     string\n}\n\ntype InternalError struct {\n    Err error\n}\n\ntype ServiceUnavailableError struct {\n    Dependency string\n}\n\ntype ConflictError struct {\n    Resource string\n    Err      error\n}\n\ntype DeletionReason string\nconst (\n    DeletionReasonIdleTimeout        DeletionReason = \"IdleTimeout\"\n    DeletionReasonMaxDurationReached DeletionReason = \"MaxDurationReached\"\n    DeletionReasonUserRequest        DeletionReason = \"UserRequest\"\n)\n```\n\n---\n\n## API Contracts\n\n### Router API (pkg/router/server.go)\n\n| Path | Method | Purpose | Request | Response |\n|------|--------|---------|---------|----------|\n| `/health/live` | GET | Liveness probe | - | `{\"status\": \"alive\"}` |\n| `/health/ready` | GET | Readiness probe | - | `{\"status\": \"ready\"}` or 503 |\n| `/v1/namespaces/:namespace/agent-runtimes/:name/invocations/*path` | GET/POST | Agent invocation proxy | Header: `x-agentcube-session-id` | Proxied response |\n| `/v1/namespaces/:namespace/code-interpreters/:name/invocations/*path` | GET/POST | Code interpreter proxy | Header: `x-agentcube-session-id` | Proxied response |\n\n#### Request Headers\n\n| Header | Required | Description |\n|--------|----------|-------------|\n| `x-agentcube-session-id` | Yes | Session identifier for sandbox routing |\n| `Authorization` | Optional | Bearer token for authentication |\n\n#### Response Headers\n\n| Header | Description |\n|--------|-------------|\n| `x-agentcube-session-id` | Echoed session ID |\n| `x-agentcube-request-id` | Request trace ID |\n\n#### Error Responses\n\n| Code | HTTP Status | Description |\n|------|-------------|-------------|\n| `SESSION_NOT_FOUND` | 404 | Session ID not found in store |\n| `NO_ENTRY_POINT` | 404 | No matching entry point for path |\n| `JWT_SIGNING_FAILED` | 500 | JWT token generation failure |\n| `INTERNAL_SERVER_ERROR` | 500 | Unexpected server error |\n\n### WorkloadManager API (pkg/workloadmanager)\n\n| Path | Method | Purpose | Request | Response |\n|------|--------|---------|---------|----------|\n| `/health/live` | GET | Liveness probe | - | `{\"status\": \"alive\"}` |\n| `/health/ready` | GET | Readiness probe | - | `{\"status\": \"ready\"}` |\n| `/sandboxes` | POST | Create sandbox | `CreateSandboxRequest` | `CreateSandboxResponse` |\n| `/sandboxes/:id` | GET | Get sandbox info | - | `SandboxInfo` |\n| `/sandboxes/:id` | DELETE | Delete sandbox | - | `{\"status\": \"deleted\"}` |\n\n#### Create Sandbox Request\n\n```json\n{\n    \"kind\": \"AgentRuntime\",\n    \"name\": \"my-agent\",\n    \"namespace\": \"default\"\n}\n```\n\n#### Create Sandbox Response\n\n```json\n{\n    \"sessionId\": \"sess-abc123\",\n    \"sandboxId\": \"sb-xyz789\",\n    \"sandboxName\": \"my-agent-sess-abc123\",\n    \"entryPoints\": [\n        {\n            \"path\": \"/api\",\n            \"protocol\": \"HTTP\",\n            \"endpoint\": \"http://10.0.0.1:8080\"\n        }\n    ]\n}\n```\n\n#### Error Response Format\n\n```json\n{\n    \"code\": \"VALIDATION_ERROR\",\n    \"message\": \"Invalid request parameter\",\n    \"details\": {\n        \"field\": \"namespace\",\n        \"reason\": \"namespace is required\"\n    }\n}\n```\n\n### PicoD API (pkg/picod/server.go)\n\n| Path | Method | Purpose | Request | Response |\n|------|--------|---------|---------|----------|\n| `/health` | GET | Health check | - | `{\"status\": \"healthy\"}` |\n| `/api/execute` | POST | Execute code | `ExecuteRequest` | `ExecuteResponse` |\n| `/api/files` | POST | Upload file | Multipart form | `{\"path\": \"...\", \"size\": ...}` |\n| `/api/files` | GET | List files | - | `FileInfo[]` |\n| `/api/files/*path` | GET | Download file | - | File content |\n\n#### Execute Request\n\n```json\n{\n    \"code\": \"print('hello')\",\n    \"language\": \"python\",\n    \"timeout\": 30\n}\n```\n\n#### Execute Response\n\n```json\n{\n    \"stdout\": \"hello\\n\",\n    \"stderr\": \"\",\n    \"exitCode\": 0,\n    \"duration\": \"0.5s\"\n}\n```\n\n#### Authentication\n\nPicoD requires JWT authentication via `Authorization: Bearer <token>` header. Tokens are validated using RSA public key.\n\n---\n\n## Error Handling\n\n### Store Errors (pkg/store/store.go)\n\n| Error | Condition | HTTP Status Mapping |\n|-------|-----------|---------------------|\n| `ErrNotFound` | Key not found in store | 404 Not Found |\n| `ErrNilSandbox` | Nil sandbox passed to StoreSandbox | 500 Internal Error |\n| `ErrZeroExpiresAt` | ExpiresAt not set | 400 Bad Request |\n| `ErrEmptySessionID` | Empty session ID | 400 Bad Request |\n| `ErrInvalidProvider` | Invalid store provider type | 500 Internal Error |\n| `ErrPasswordRequired` | Redis password required but not provided | 500 Internal Error |\n| `ErrKeyNotExists` | Key does not exist | 404 Not Found |\n| `ErrSessionExists` | Session already exists | 409 Conflict |\n\n### Router Errors (pkg/router/errors.go)\n\n```go\ntype APIStatus interface {\n    Status() int\n    Code() string\n    Message() string\n}\n\ntype RouterError struct {\n    status  int\n    code    string\n    message string\n}\n```\n\n| Code | HTTP Status | Description |\n|------|-------------|-------------|\n| `SESSION_NOT_FOUND` | 404 | Session not found in store |\n| `SANDBOX_NOT_FOUND` | 404 | Sandbox pod not found |\n| `NO_ENTRY_POINT` | 404 | No entry point matches request path |\n| `CONCURRENCY_LIMIT` | 429 | Too many concurrent requests |\n| `JWT_SIGNING_FAILED` | 500 | JWT generation error |\n| `STORE_ERROR` | 500 | Store operation error |\n| `PROXY_ERROR` | 502 | Reverse proxy error |\n| `INTERNAL_ERROR` | 500 | Unexpected error |\n\n### JWT Errors (pkg/router)\n\n| Error Type | Condition |\n|------------|-----------|\n| `JWTKeyLoadError` | Failed to load RSA key |\n| `JWTValidationError` | Token validation failed |\n| `JWTGenerationError` | Token generation failed |\n\n### WorkloadManager Errors (pkg/workloadmanager/types.go)\n\n| Error Type | HTTP Status | Condition |\n|------------|-------------|-----------|\n| `ValidationError` | 400 | Invalid request parameters |\n| `NotFoundError` | 404 | Resource not found |\n| `ServiceUnavailableError` | 503 | Dependency unavailable |\n| `InternalError` | 500 | Unexpected server error |\n| `ConflictError` | 409 | Resource conflict |\n\n### Error Handling Pattern\n\n```go\nfunc HandleError(w http.ResponseWriter, _ *http.Request, err error) {\n    w.Header().Set(\"Content-Type\", \"application/json\")\n    \n    var resp ErrorResponse\n    var status int\n    \n    switch e := err.(type) {\n    case *ValidationError:\n        status = http.StatusBadRequest\n        resp = ErrorResponse{\n            Code:    \"VALIDATION_ERROR\",\n            Message: \"Invalid request parameter\",\n            Details: map[string]string{\"field\": e.Field, \"reason\": e.Reason},\n        }\n    case *NotFoundError:\n        status = http.StatusNotFound\n        resp = ErrorResponse{\n            Code:    \"NOT_FOUND\",\n            Message: e.Error(),\n        }\n    case *ServiceUnavailableError:\n        status = http.StatusServiceUnavailable\n        resp = ErrorResponse{\n            Code:    \"SERVICE_UNAVAILABLE\",\n            Message: e.Error(),\n        }\n    case *InternalError:\n        status = http.StatusInternalServerError\n        resp = ErrorResponse{\n            Code:    \"INTERNAL_ERROR\",\n            Message: \"Unexpected server error\",\n        }\n    default:\n        status = http.StatusInternalServerError\n        resp = ErrorResponse{\n            Code:    \"INTERNAL_ERROR\",\n            Message: \"Unexpected server error\",\n        }\n    }\n    \n    w.WriteHeader(status)\n    json.NewEncoder(w).Encode(resp)\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## Testing Strategy\n\n### Unit Tests\n\n#### Router Tests (pkg/router/*_test.go)\n\n| Test File | Coverage |\n|-----------|----------|\n| `server_test.go` | Server initialization, route registration, health endpoints |\n| `jwt_test.go` | JWT generation, validation, refresh, key management |\n| `session_manager_test.go` | Session lookup, K8s client integration |\n| `reverse_proxy_test.go` | Proxy director, response modification, error handling |\n| `middleware_test.go` | Concurrency limit, logging, recovery middleware |\n| `errors_test.go` | Error response formatting, APIStatus interface |\n| `config_test.go` | Configuration validation, defaults |\n\n#### WorkloadManager Tests (pkg/workloadmanager/*_test.go)\n\n| Test File | Coverage |\n|-----------|----------|\n| `server_test.go` | HTTP server lifecycle, graceful shutdown |\n| `router_test.go` | Chi router setup, route registration |\n| `types_test.go` | Error types, response structures |\n| `store_test.go` | Memory store operations |\n| `k8s_client_test.go` | K8s client CRUD operations |\n| `lifecycle_test.go` | Sandbox lifecycle management |\n| `garbage_collector_test.go` | GC intervals, timeout handling |\n| `informers_test.go` | CRD informer setup |\n| `handlers/*_test.go` | Health, sandbox CRUD handlers |\n| `middleware/*_test.go` | CORS, logging, recovery middleware |\n| `benchmark_test.go` | Performance benchmarks |\n\n#### Store Tests (pkg/store/*_test.go)\n\n| Test File | Coverage |\n|-----------|----------|\n| `store_test.go` | Store interface, error types |\n| `valkey_test.go` | Valkey client operations, TTL handling |\n\n#### PicoD Tests (pkg/picod/*_test.go)\n\n| Test File | Coverage |\n|-----------|----------|\n| `picod_test.go` | Server lifecycle, endpoint handling |\n| `auth_test.go` | JWT authentication middleware |\n\n#### CRD Types Tests (pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/*_test.go)\n\n| Test File | Coverage |\n|-----------|----------|\n| `types_test.go` | CRD type validation, default values |\n\n### Integration Tests\n\n#### E2E Tests (test/e2e/e2e_test.go)\n\n| Test | Description |\n|------|-------------|\n| Sandbox creation | Full sandbox lifecycle: create → invoke → delete |\n| Session routing | Router proxy to sandbox pod |\n| Health checks | All component health endpoints |\n| Idle cleanup | Agentd controller cleanup verification |\n\n#### Test Framework (test/e2e/framework/)\n\n| File | Purpose |\n|------|---------|\n| `fixture_manager.go` | Test fixture setup/teardown |\n| `http_client.go` | HTTP client for API testing |\n| `kube_client.go` | Kubernetes client for CRD operations |\n| `wait_helpers.go` | Polling and wait utilities |\n| `test_context.go` | Test configuration and context |\n\n### Test Coverage Requirements\n\n| Package | Target Coverage |\n|---------|-----------------|\n| `pkg/router` | ≥80% |\n| `pkg/workloadmanager` | ≥80% |\n| `pkg/store` | ≥80% |\n| `pkg/picod` | ≥70% |\n| `pkg/agentd` | ≥70% |\n| `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1` | ≥60% |\n| `pkg/common/types` | ≥90% |\n\n### Benchmarks\n\n```go\n// JWT Performance Benchmarks (pkg/router/jwt_test.go)\nfunc BenchmarkJWTGenerateToken(b *testing.B)\nfunc BenchmarkJWTValidateToken(b *testing.B)\nfunc BenchmarkJWTGenerateTokenPair(b *testing.B)\n\n// WorkloadManager Benchmarks (pkg/workloadmanager/benchmark_test.go)\nfunc BenchmarkSandboxLifecycle(b *testing.B)\nfunc BenchmarkGarbageCollector(b *testing.B)\n```\n\n---\n\n## File Structure\n\n```\nagentcube/\n├── cmd/\n│   ├── agentd/main.go           # Agentd CLI entry point\n│   ├── agentcube/main.go        # Unified CLI entry point\n│   ├── picod/main.go            # PicoD CLI entry point\n│   └───────────────────────────────\n│\n├── pkg/\n│   ├── agentd/\n│   │   ├── idle_cleanup.go      # Idle cleanup controller\n│   │   ├── idle_cleanup_test.go\n│   │   ├── defaults.go          # Default configuration\n│   │   └───────────────────────────\n│   │\n│   ├── apis/runtime/v1alpha1/\n│   │   ├── agentruntime_types.go      # AgentRuntime CRD\n│   │   ├── codeinterpreter_types.go   # CodeInterpreter CRD\n│   │   ├── shared_types.go            # Common types, constants\n│   │   ├── register.go                # Scheme registration\n│   │   ├── groupversion_info.go       # API group info\n│   │   ├── zz_generated.deepcopy.go   # Deep copy implementation\n│   │   └───────────────────────────────────\n│   │\n│   ├── common/types/\n│   │   ├── sandbox.go            # Sandbox info, request/response types\n│   │   └───────────────────────────────\n│   │\n│   ├── picod/\n│   │   ├── server.go             # HTTP server setup\n│   │   ├── config.go             # Configuration\n│   │   ├── auth.go               # JWT authentication\n│   │   ├── execute.go            # Code execution handler\n│   │   ├── files.go              # File I/O handlers\n│   │   ├── sanitize.go           # Path sanitization\n│   │   ├── health.go             # Health check\n│   │   └───────────────────────────────\n│   │\n│   ├── router/\n│   │   ├── server.go             # Gin HTTP server\n│   │   ├── config.go             # Router configuration\n│   │   ├── session_manager.go    # Session management\n│   │   ├── reverse_proxy.go      # Reverse proxy logic\n│   │   ├── jwt.go                # JWT management (implicit from tests)\n│   │   ├── middleware.go         # Concurrency, logging, recovery\n│   │   ├── errors.go             # Error types and responses\n│   │   └───────────────────────────────────\n│   │\n│   ├── store/\n│   │   ├── store.go              # Store interface\n│   │   ├── store_redis.go        # Redis implementation\n│   │   ├── store_valkey.go       # Valkey implementation\n│   │   └───────────────────────────────\n│   │\n│   ├── workloadmanager/\n│   │   ├── server.go             # Chi HTTP server\n│   │   ├── router.go             # Route setup\n│   │   ├── config.go             # Configuration\n│   │   ├── types.go              # Error/response types\n│   │   ├── k8s_client.go         # Kubernetes client\n│   │   ├── store.go              # Memory store\n│   │   ├── lifecycle.go          # Sandbox lifecycle manager\n│   │   ├── garbage_collector.go  # Garbage collector\n│   │   ├── informers.go          # CRD informers\n│   │   ├── defaults.go           # Default values\n│   │   ├── handlers/\n│   │   │   ├── handler.go        # Handler interface\n│   │   │   ├── health.go         # Health endpoints\n│   │   │   ├── sandbox_delete.go # Sandbox deletion\n│   │   │   └─────────────────────────────\n│   │   ├── middleware/\n│   │   │   ├── cors.go           # CORS middleware\n│   │   │   ├── logging.go        # Request logging\n│   │   │   ├── recovery.go       # Panic recovery\n│   │   │   └─────────────────────────────\n│   │   └───────────────────────────────────\n│   │\n│   └───────────────────────────────────────\n│\n├── client-go/\n│   ├── clientset/versioned/\n│   │   ├── clientset.go          # Typed client\n│   │   ├── fake/                 # Fake client for testing\n│   │   └───────────────────────────────\n│   ├── informers/externalversions/\n│   │   ├── runtime/v1alpha1/\n│   │   │   ├── agentruntime.go   # AgentRuntime informer\n│   │   │   ├── codeinterpreter.go # CodeInterpreter informer\n│   │   │   └───────────────────────────────\n│   │   └───────────────────────────────\n│   └───────────────────────────────────────\n│\n├── manifests/charts/base/\n│   ├── crds/\n│   │   ├── runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_agentruntimes.yaml\n│   │   ├── runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_codeinterpreters.yaml\n│   │   └───────────────────────────────\n│   ├── templates/\n│   │   ├── agentcube-router.yaml\n│   │   ├── workloadmanager.yaml\n│   │   ├── rbac-router.yaml\n│   │   ├── rbac/workloadmanager.yaml\n│   │   └───────────────────────────────\n│   ├── Chart.yaml\n│   ├── values.yaml\n│   └───────────────────────────────────────\n│\n├── sdk-python/\n│   └───────────────────────────────────────\n│\n├── docs/\n│   ├── docs/\n│   │   ├── architecture/\n│   │   │   ├── overview.md\n│   │   │   ├── components.md\n│   │   │   ├── crds.md\n│   │   │   ├── session-flow.md\n│   │   │   ├── data-flow.md\n│   │   │   └───────────────────────────────\n│   │   ├── api/\n│   │   │   ├── router/openapi.yaml\n│   │   │   ├── workloadmanager/openapi.yaml\n│   │   │   ├── picod/openapi.yaml\n│   │   │   ├── sdk-python/\n│   │   │   ├── client-go/\n│   │   │   ├── crds/\n│   │   │   └───────────────────────────────\n│   │   └───────────────────────────────\n│   ├── docusaurus.config.ts\n│   └───────────────────────────────────────\n│\n├── test/e2e/\n│   ├── e2e_test.go\n│   ├── framework/\n│   │   ├── fixture_manager.go\n│   │   ├── http_client.go\n│   │   ├── kube_client.go\n│   │   ├── wait_helpers.go\n│   │   ├── test_context.go\n│   │   └───────────────────────────────\n│   ├── kind-config.yaml\n│   └───────────────────────────────────────\n│\n├── .github/workflows/\n│   ├── main.yml                 # Main CI pipeline\n│   ├── e2e.yml                  # E2E tests\n│   ├── test-coverage.yml        # Coverage reporting\n│   ├── python-sdk-tests.yml     # Python SDK tests\n│   └───────────────────────────────────────\n│\n├── design.md                    # System design document\n├── project.md                   # Project context\n├── proposal.md                  # Overall proposal\n│\n└──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n```\n\n---\n\n## Dependencies\n\n### Go Dependencies\n\n| Package | Version | Purpose |\n|---------|---------|---------|\n| `github.com/gin-gonic/gin` | v1.x | HTTP framework (Router, PicoD) |\n| `github.com/go-chi/chi/v5` | v5.x | HTTP framework (WorkloadManager) |\n| `k8s.io/klog/v2` | v2.x | Structured logging |\n| `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime` | v0.19.x | Controller utilities (Agentd) |\n| `k8s.io/apimachinery` | v0.x | K8s API types |\n| `k8s.io/client-go` | v0.x | K8s client library |\n| `github.com/golang-jwt/jwt/v5` | v5.x | JWT handling |\n| `github.com/go-redis/redis/v9` | v9.x | Redis client |\n| `github.com/valkey-io/valkey-go` | latest | Valkey client |\n| `github.com/spf13/pflag` | v1.x | POSIX-style flags |\n\n### Python Dependencies (sdk-python)\n\n| Package | Version | Purpose |\n|---------|---------|---------|\n| `typer` | >=0.9 | CLI framework |\n| `httpx` | >=0.24 | HTTP client |\n| `pydantic` | >=2.0 | Data validation |\n\n### Documentation Dependencies\n\n| Package | Version | Purpose |\n|---------|---------|---------|\n| `docusaurus` | 3.x | Documentation site framework |\n| `mermaid` | >=10.x | Diagram rendering |\n\n---\n\n## Implementation Notes\n\n### Key Design Decisions\n\n1. **Dual HTTP Frameworks**: Router/PicoD use Gin for rich middleware support; WorkloadManager uses Chi for lightweight routing with Handler interface pattern.\n\n2. **Store Abstraction**: Unified `Store` interface supports both Redis and Valkey backends, enabling backend swap without code changes.\n\n3. **CRD-Based Configuration**: AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter CRDs define sandbox templates, enabling declarative configuration via K8s.\n\n4. **Warm Pool Support**: CodeInterpreter supports `warmPoolSize` for pre-warmed instances, reducing cold-start latency.\n\n5. **JWT RS256**: Router generates JWT tokens with RSA-2048 keys, supporting key rotation and secret storage in K8s.\n\n6. **Controller-runtime for Agentd**: Idle cleanup uses controller-runtime with leader election for HA deployments.\n\n7. **Graceful Shutdown**: All HTTP servers support graceful shutdown with configurable timeouts.\n\n### Session Flow\n\n```\nClient Request → Router\n    ↓\n[1] Extract session-id from header\n    ↓\n[2] Query Store for sandbox mapping\n    ↓\n[3] Build target URL from entry point\n    ↓\n[4] Generate JWT for sandbox auth (if required)\n    ↓\n[5] Reverse proxy to sandbox pod\n    ↓\n[6] Update last activity timestamp\n    ↓\nResponse to Client\n```\n\n### Sandbox Lifecycle\n\n```\nCreateSandboxRequest → WorkloadManager\n    ↓\n[1] Validate request (kind, name, namespace)\n    ↓\n[2] Get CRD (AgentRuntime/CodeInterpreter)\n    ↓\n[3] Generate session-id and sandbox name\n    ↓\n[4] Create Pod with labels/annotations\n    ↓\n[5] Create ServiceAccount (if needed)\n    ↓\n[6] Create Secret for JWT public key (if needed)\n    ↓\n[7] Store session → sandbox mapping in Redis\n    ↓\n[8] Return CreateSandboxResponse\n    ↓\nSession Active (proxy via Router)\n    ↓\nIdle Timeout / Max Duration → Agentd Cleanup\n    ↓\nDelete Pod, cleanup Store entry\n```\n\n---\n\n## References\n\n- Spec: `changes/AR-043/spec.md`\n- Delta Spec: `changes/AR-043/delta-spec.md`\n- Proposal: `changes/AR-043/proposal.md`\n- Tasks: `changes/AR-043/tasks.md`\n- Design Document: `design.md`\n- Project Context: `project.md`\n- Router Package: `pkg/router/`\n- WorkloadManager Package: `pkg/workloadmanager/`\n- PicoD Package: `pkg/picod/`\n- Agentd Package: `pkg/agentd/`\n- Store Package: `pkg/store/`\n- CRD Types: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`\n- Python SDK: `sdk-python/`\n- client-go: `client-go/`\n- Docusaurus Documentation: https://docusaurus.io/docs\n- OpenAPI Specification 3.0: https://spec.openapis.org/oas/v3.0.0\n- Mermaid Documentation: https://mermaid.js.org/\n- Kubernetes API conventions: https://github.com/kubernetes/community/blob/master/contributors/devel/sig-architecture/api-conventions.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.\n\nLSP errors detected in other files:\n<diagnostics file=\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/cmd/internal/cli/logging.go\">\nERROR [6:2] could not import k8s.io/klog/v2 (no required module provides package \"k8s.io/klog/v2\")\nERROR [10:2] undefined: klog\n</diagnostics>\n\nLSP errors detected in other files:\n<diagnostics file=\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/client-go/clientset/versioned/fake/register.go\">\nERROR [20:18] could not import github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1 (no required module provides package \"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1\")\nERROR [22:2] could not import k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime/schema (no required module provides package \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime/schema\")\nERROR [23:2] could not import k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime/serializer (no requir